{"tid":912680,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港鐵 QR Code 二維碼付費乘車服務加碼！2021 年支援 TNG．銀聯．WeChat Pay HK","createTime":"2018-11-23T01:06:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-23T06:06:21.000Z","uid":41818,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"90ff7189ea663f8b7d713af46bd8c39c6917c1c2","tid":912680,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T01:06:54.000Z","msg":"早前港鐵 MTR 正式確認，批出合約予 AlipayHK 支付寶香港於港鐵出入閘機提供 QR Code 二維碼付費乘車服務，最快可於 2020 年年中使用後，港鐵再公布跟 3 間二維碼服務供應商，包括：TNG、銀聯（Union Pay）、WeChat Pay HK 批出合約，預計 2021 年年中投入服務。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵公司表示，希望透過引進更多服務供應商，為顧客提供更多元化的付費方式，能因應使用需要而選擇，使乘車過程更為便捷。其實港鐵批出 QR Code 二維碼付費乘車服務合約予 TNG、銀聯、WeChat Pay HK，也未必無因，因為當系統建成後，港鐵可引入更多服務提供者使用該系統。只是當中會率先對應 AlipayHK，而 TNG、銀聯、WeChat Pay HK 則緊隨其後地開通相關服務。同樣地，QR Code 二維碼付費乘車服務適用於港鐵市區鐵路網絡，惟機場快線車站及輕鐵則不包括在內。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2KpWonV\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2KpWonV&d=GQ6U6nUhNHM%2B9feMnVYy7ttKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=539221e4\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2KpWonV</a>"},{"pid":"cb76d91d51a26fc101ee3c6d74e0135d8ee1d96b","tid":912680,"uid":30085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T01:07:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24381b6abac03ae01cbd5d54de8a6d5a3f950ab2","tid":912680,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T01:09:36.000Z","msg":"痴撚線，地鐵日日打交都似"},{"pid":"2b0d57c3c18d7d9abfcc7d195dc76d39b5192fc9","tid":912680,"uid":66839,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T01:10:13.000Z","msg":"點解冇applepay"},{"pid":"e4fadf6a3885a19f07f8c967613cb6a28436c0e4","tid":912680,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T01:10:31.000Z","msg":"全部中資<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b2fceddc877dfa2b603d46d21f9d30c3094c7be","tid":912680,"uid":18251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2b0d57c3